subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: After losing the opening set against the fifth-seeded Nadia Petrova of Russia, Serena Williams summoned the power and belief of Grand Slams past to win her third round match, 1-6, 7-5, 6-3.
